dummy
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:In NZ from the time land laws were applied, one paid to acquire the title to a parcel of Crown land on behalf of another who was not legally entitled to do so; one who acquires title to land in name only, on behalf of another.
Origin:
